entry.summary:
BlockBeats news, on August 27, the developer community OpenBuild announced the winning projects of the main track of the ETH Shenzhen hackathon, as follows:


· The winning project of the innovative Dapps track is Nextmate.ai;
· The winning projects of the Source tool/infrastructure track are Ethereum Colored Address Protocol, Web3Insights, and Fat Preconf DApp;
· The winning projects of the xFi track are Mars protocol, Outrun, and UbiBank;
· The winning projects of the General track are ChainWhiz, Youbet Task, and Xfinder.


This ETH Shenzhen hackathon has set up 4 main tracks and 5 Bounty tracks, with a prize pool of more than 50,000 US dollars, and has received sponsorship support from projects such as the Ethereum Foundation, Fuel Labs, Morph, Chainlink, Vara Network, SmartLayer, and Bifrost.
